comment: /**  * Return the HTTP request method that caused the failure.  */
code: /**  * Return the HTTP request method that caused the failure.  */ public String getMethod() {     return this.method. }

comment: /**  * Return the actually supported HTTP methods, or {@code null} if not known.  */
code: /**  * Return the actually supported HTTP methods, or {@code null} if not known.  */ @Nullable public String[] getSupportedMethods() {     return this.supportedMethods. }

comment: /**  * Return the actually supported HTTP methods as {@link HttpMethod} instances,  * or {@code null} if not known.  * @since 3.2  */
code: /**  * Return the actually supported HTTP methods as {@link HttpMethod} instances,  * or {@code null} if not known.  * @since 3.2  */ @Nullable public Set<HttpMethod> getSupportedHttpMethods() {     if (this.supportedMethods == null) {         return null.     }     List<HttpMethod> supportedMethods = new LinkedList<>().     for (String value : this.supportedMethods) {         HttpMethod resolved = HttpMethod.resolve(value).         if (resolved != null) {             supportedMethods.add(resolved).         }     }     return EnumSet.copyOf(supportedMethods). }
